OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FEvidence has been submitted to Cumbria
OL,7,FPolice in connection with allegations
OL,8,Fof historical abuse at a church-run
OL,9,Fmother and baby institution where more
OL,10,Fthan 60 newborn babies died, following
OL,11,Fan ITV News investigation.
OL,13,FA new report by Dr Michael Lambert, an
OL,14,Fhistorian of the welfare state at
OL,15,FLancaster University, has outlined a
OL,16,Fhigh infant death rate at St Monica's
OL,17,Fhome in Kendal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FThe report concluded that the deaths
OL,7,Fwere due to a combination of failings,
OL,8,Fincluding inadequate facilities,
OL,9,Fmalpractice and poor care from those
OL,10,Fdelivering babies and a lack of
OL,11,Foversight from the church and state.
OL,13,FAnalysis of public health records,
OL,14,Falongside birth and death
OL,15,Fcertificates, indicated that children
OL,16,Fwith disabilities born at the mother
OL,17,Fand baby home were deemed "un-
OL,18,Fadoptable" and denied modern medical
OL,19,Fcare, according to the new research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FUnmarried pregnant women from across
OL,7,Fthe north of England were sent to St
OL,8,FMonica's, which was run by the Diocese
OL,9,Fof Carlisle, to give birth in secret
OL,10,Ffrom 1917 until its closure in 1970.
OL,12,FThese latest revelations come after an
OL,13,FITV News Freedom of Information
OL,14,FRequest in 2024 obtained burial
OL,15,Frecords which showed that 43 babies,
OL,16,Fwho were born and then died at the
OL,17,Fhome, were buried in mass unmarked
OL,18,Fgraves in secret, alongside two
OL,19,Fmothers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FAnd now more fatalities have been
OL,7,Fidentified.
OL,9,FDr Lambert's report detailed an
OL,10,Fadditional 18 infant deaths, taking
OL,11,Fthe total to 61, and 54 stillbirths.
OL,12,FIt remains unclear where these babies
OL,13,Fare buried.
OL,15,FAn ITV News investigation found there
OL,16,Fwere hundreds of mass unmarked graves
OL,17,Fof babies in cemeteries across
OL,18,FEngland, from Newcastle to Hampshire
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FDr Lambert said numerous warnings
OL,7,Fabout sub-standard care over many
OL,8,Fyears "were not acted upon" by the
OL,9,Fhealth authorities who subsidised the
OL,10,Fhome and the Anglican bodies involved
OL,11,Fin its governance.
OL,13,F"These represent a failure by the
OL,14,FChurch of England to discharge its
OL,15,Fresponsibility over all the mother and
OL,16,Fbaby homes run in its name," he told
OL,17,FITV News.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
