OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,F"And the UK government whose system of
OL,7,Ffunding and inspections was wholly
OL,8,Fineffective in ensuring unmarried
OL,9,Fmothers were cared for."
OL,11,FWhat happened at St Monica's was
OL,12,Femblematic of a system operating
OL,13,Facross Britain.
OL,15,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,16,Faffected by this issue or has a story
OL,17,Fto share, you can get in touch by
OL,18,Femailing: socialaffairs@itv.com
OL,26,@qD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
