OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FBetween 1949 and the mid-1970s, an
OL,7,Festimated 200,000 unmarried women were
OL,8,Fsent away to mother and baby homes run
OL,9,Fby churches and the state, where they
OL,10,Fwere pressured and coerced into giving
OL,11,Fup their babies for adoption. Other
OL,12,Finfants died due to poor care.
OL,14,FOur long-running ITV News
OL,15,Finvestigation has exposed a culture of
OL,16,Fcruelty and neglect at these
OL,17,Finstitutions, driven by the societal
OL,18,Fbelief that unmarried women were unfit
OL,19,Fto be mothers and deserved to be
OL,20,Fpunished.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FFamilies are still living with the
OL,7,Fconsequences of that cruelty today.
OL,9,FThe Lancaster University report
OL,10,Ffocused on the life and death of
OL,11,FStephen Holt who died aged three
OL,12,Fmonths old at St Monica's in 1964.
OL,14,FHis mother Judith was 17 and unmarried
OL,15,Fwhen she gave birth to Stephen, but it
OL,16,Fsoon became clear he was very unwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FDr Lambert said the baby boy was born
OL,7,Fwith spina bifida and later denied
OL,8,Fmedical treatment and "instead left or
OL,9,Fencouraged to die given its assumed
OL,10,Finevitability".
OL,12,F"Because he was born with a
OL,13,Fdisability, this made Stephen
OL,14,F'unadoptable', as such children -
OL,15,Fincluding those of mixed heritage -
OL,16,Fwere seen as a burden rather than a
OL,17,Fblessing," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,F"Being 'unadoptable', and the
OL,7,Falternative being local authority care
OL,8,Fand a cost to the public purse,
OL,9,FStephen was denied advances in modern
OL,10,Fmedical care afforded to legitimate
OL,11,Fchildren and effectively allowed to
OL,12,Fdie.
OL,14,F"He was not the only infant to die
OL,15,Fwith a treatable condition in the
OL,16,Fhome."
OL,18,FFor more than 20 years, Stephen's step-
OL,19,FDad, Stephen Hindley, has been
OL,20,Fsearching for the truth.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
