CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FLast year he told ITV News that his
OL,7,Fwife Judith never recovered from the
OL,8,Ftrauma and abuse she endured at St
OL,9,FMonica's, and in 2006, she took her
OL,10,Fown life close to the cemetery where
OL,11,Fher baby is buried.
OL,13,FThe Lancaster University report
OL,14,Fconcluded that staffing issues and the
OL,15,Fhome's long-serving matron, whose
OL,16,F"maternity care and culture was stuck
OL,17,Fin time", resembling a standard of
OL,18,Ftreatment from the 1930s, bore
OL,19,Fsignificant responsibility for the
OL,20,Fhigh infant death rate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
