OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FThese revelations will increase
OL,7,Fpressure on the Church of England to
OL,8,Fofficially apologise for its role in
OL,9,Fthe wider forced adoption scandal and
OL,10,Fprovide support to victims.
OL,12,FIt is currently consulting with
OL,13,Fsurvivor groups on the wording and
OL,14,Fformat of that apology, which is
OL,15,Fexpected as early as this summer.
OL,17,FThe church operated and funded 107
OL,18,Fmother and baby homes and had over 30
OL,19,Fadoption agencies over a period of
OL,20,Ffour decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FIn March the Prime Minister Keir
OL,7,FStarmer told ITV News that his
OL,8,F"instinct" was to issue a government
OL,9,Fapology as the state played a central
OL,10,Frole in these adoption practices.
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer told ITV News in
OL,13,FMarch that 'his instinct' is to issue
OL,14,Fa government apology for the state's
OL,15,Frole in the forced adoption scandal
OL,17,FCumbria Police told ITV News that it
OL,18,F"welcomed" the report received from Dr
OL,19,FLambert, and it is now being reviewed
OL,20,Fby senior officers within the force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
