PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: 'We understand
OL,7,Fthat although the practices occurred
OL,8,Fseveral decades ago, those who
OL,9,Fsuffered or have been affected by the
OL,10,Fpractices - including immediate family
OL,11,Fmembers ` will continue to be affected
OL,12,Fand concerned. As such, we always
OL,13,Fwelcome any new information."
OL,15,FThe Diocese of Carlisle said in a
OL,16,Fstatement: "We continue to offer our
OL,17,Fheartfelt apologies to those people
OL,18,Faffected by accounts of malpractice at
OL,19,Fthe home, which closed in 1970.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
