CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781075106
OL,3,CEvidence sent to Cumbria Police about
OL,4,C61 baby deaths at church-run home
OL,6,F"Their testimonies are truly shocking,
OL,7,Fand our prayers remain with all those
OL,8,Faffected, directly or indirectly. We
OL,9,Fare committed to work with full
OL,10,Ftransparency in support of any
OL,11,Fsubsequent police investigation.
OL,13,F"Each child and mother at St Monica's
OL,14,Fdeserved the utmost care. One
OL,15,Favoidable death was one too many.
OL,17,F"Cruel or incompetent practice should
OL,18,Fhave been prevented. Any behaviour
OL,19,Fwhich countered this was
OL,20,Freprehensible."
